groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: Pennsbury 24
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: This cache is located in the Pennsbury Township Park
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description: This is a green ammo box filled with extra nice goodies such as stickers, pens, beads, and other stuff for young and old. Title refers to its date of placement: our 24th Anniversary. (Those who geocache together, stay together!) Park in the lot for the Pennsbury Township Park and proceed into the park area behind the parking area.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:encoded_hints: Down the slope to the back of the field, trail to the right, look along the right side of the trail.

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: Quick find with dawnie22 and kids
